      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-10-13T18:26:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": ":(\n\nI was hoping we’d lift the limit on value length altogether. No?\n\nI envision uses where 2k won’t be sufficient. Your PAGE_SIZE example usage is bigger than 2k on all of the systems we care about, for example.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 61,
        "startChar": 26,
