        "id": 1144624
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-10-13T22:33:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think all root annotation objects need a name to make them identifiable on the reporting end. For sequences, the value would point to an array of some other (POD) object type.",
      "parentUuid": "c4527643_afbd5568",
      "revId": "8ea2b5e2f1f00ab7062a34d722909c4581c7dd93",
